            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A Canadian man’s beloved classic Ford truck has been recovered, all thanks to a tip submitted by a Facebook user. Back on June 10, the owner of the pickup took it to the Kamloops Golf & Country Club in British Columbia, parking it while doing a round of golf. However, when he was done the Ford was nowhere to be found.",
